text.tspan: Newspaper
Biddly boodly blorp. Yammer Yammer. All
this chunk of text needs to accomplish is
to look like a chunk of text. It thus does not
matter what I write here. On the other hand,
a few of you are probably going to zoom in
and read it, so I guess I'll put some juicy info
in here while I'm at it: The design for
Colin is a non-horrific version of the creepy
mannequins in a horror video game called
Timore. The creature in the picture behind
the cashier is known as The Unigoat, a cute
little megalomaniacal fusion of a unicorn and
goat, that lives to advise you on how to live
your life. Some unused easter eggs of it can
be found in the files of my FNaF fangame.
If you read this, feel free to comment
"#Unigoat" to let me know. Thank you for
paying such close atten-
tion! :)
